alhost/travelguide/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/index.jpg" alt="index" width="169" height="127" />It''s distance is about 35 km from Dhaka city at Savar.It built in memory of millions who died in the liberation war in 1971.This 50 m. high and beautifully monument''s structure was designed by the famous architect Mr.Moinul Hossain.In liberation time about 3 million peoples had died so for this memory,Government dicided to build a memorial monument in Savar.</p>', 'Dhaka District', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '72-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-10 00:36:04', '2016-02-09 18:36:04', '', 72, 'http://localhost/travelguide/index.php/2016/02/10/72-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
