ocalhost/travelguide/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/back-side-from-zia-uddan-300x225.jpg" alt="back-side-from-zia-uddan" width="169" height="127" />One of a nice place to see in Dhaka. This is in central Dhaka. By Bus it will take from Airport to Parliament House not more than 20 Minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><span style="color: #000080;"><strong> </strong></span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Dhaka District', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '72-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-10 10:20:59', '2016-02-10 04:20:59', '', 72, 'http://localhost/travelguide/index.php/2016/02/10/72-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
