" width="169" height="127" />The Novo Theatre</strong> </span>is situated right in the heart of Dhaka city and it’s a nice place to visit especially if you have kids with you. It’s a planetarium theater . They have a large Dome shaped gallery , where 3D movie is shown. The 3D movie is projected on the large Dome shaped ceiling of the gallery hall.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="heading_name_wrapper">\r\n<h2 class="heading_name "><span style="color: #000080;"><strong>National Parliament House</strong></span></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><img class=" wp-image-111 alignleft" src="http://localhost/travelguide/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/back-side-from-zia-uddan-300x225.jpg" alt="back-side-from-zia-uddan" width="169" height="127" />One of a nice place to see in Dhaka. This is in central Dhaka. By Bus it will take from Airport to Parliament House not more than 20 Minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2><span style="color: #000080;"><strong> </strong></span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Dhaka District', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '72-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-10 10:23:33', '2016-02-10 04:23:33', '', 72, 'http://localhost/travelguide/index.php/2016/02/10/72-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
